SELECT TOP (1000) [Id]
      ,'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' as [CreatedById]
      ,GETDATE() as [CreatedOn]
      ,NULL as [UpdatedById]
      ,NULL as [UpdatedOn]
      ,[Name]
      ,[IsDisabled]
      ,[SortOrder]
      ,[Code]
      ,[Description]
      ,[ParentId]
      ,[Email]
      ,[SendEmail]
      ,[AddressTo]
      ,[CCEmail]
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[Agencies]
  
  ORDER BY ParentId

SELECT 
    u.[Id],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] = 'FB95044D-9942-480E-BD1E-1F9EE9BF1EB3' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE u.[CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.IsDisabled = 0 THEN 'Active'
		ELSE 'Disabled'
	  END AS [Status],
    NULL AS [UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    NULL AS [ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    u.CreatedOn,
    urd.UserId,
    ua.AgencyId, 
    STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') AS Roles,
    CASE 
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%System Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial Reporter%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Agency Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Analyst%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Manager%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister Assistant%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Executive Director%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%View Only Properties%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002'
	   
    END AS UserType
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        ur.UserId,
        MAX(ur.CreatedOn) AS CreatedOn,
        STRING_AGG(r.Name, ', ') AS RoleName
    FROM [pims].[dbo].[UserRoles] ur
    INNER JOIN Roles r ON ur.RoleId = r.Id
    GROUP BY ur.UserId
) AS urd ON u.Id = urd.UserId

LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT UserId, MIN(AgencyId) AS AgencyId
    FROM UserAgencies
    GROUP BY UserId
) ua_min ON u.Id = ua_min.UserId
LEFT OUTER JOIN UserAgencies ua ON u.Id = ua.UserId AND ua.AgencyId = ua_min.AgencyId

WHERE u.Id <> '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'

GROUP BY u.[Id],
    u.[CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    u.CreatedOn, 
    urd.UserId, 
    ua.AgencyId
ORDER BY u.CreatedOn, u.UpdatedOn

SELECT [ParcelId]
      ,YEAR([Date]) AS [Date]
      ,[Key]
      ,
	  CASE 
		WHEN [CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE [CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[UpdatedById]
      ,[UpdatedOn]
      ,[Firm]
      ,[Value]
      ,[Note]
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[ParcelEvaluations]

SELECT [ParcelId]
      ,[FiscalYear]
      ,[Key]
      ,CASE 
		WHEN [CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE [CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[UpdatedById]
      ,[UpdatedOn]
      ,[Value]
      ,[Note]
      ,[EffectiveDate]
  FROM [dbo].[ParcelFiscals]

  CreatedOn,
  UpdatedById,
  UpdatedOn,
  [Value],

  FROM BuildingFiscals 
  
WHERE BuildingId IN (

SELECT [Id]

	  END AS [CreatedById]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[UpdatedById]
      ,[UpdatedOn]
      ,[ProjectId]
      ,[NoteType]
      ,[Note]
  FROM [dbo].[ProjectNotes]

SELECT TOP (1000) [Id]
      ,'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' as [CreatedById]
      ,GETDATE() as [CreatedOn]
      ,[UpdatedById]
      ,[UpdatedOn]
      ,[Name]
      ,[IsDisabled]
      ,[SortOrder]
      ,[Code]
      ,[Description]
      ,[ParentId]
      ,[Email]
      ,[SendEmail]
      ,[AddressTo]
      ,[CCEmail]
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[Agencies]
  
  ORDER BY ParentId

SELECT 
    u.[Id],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] = 'FB95044D-9942-480E-BD1E-1F9EE9BF1EB3' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE u.[CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.IsDisabled = 0 THEN 'Active'
		ELSE 'Disabled'
	  END AS [Status],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    u.CreatedOn,
    urd.UserId,
    ua.AgencyId, 
    STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') AS Roles,
    CASE 
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%System Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial Reporter%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Agency Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Analyst%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Manager%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister Assistant%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Executive Director%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%View Only Properties%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002'
	   
    END AS UserType
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        ur.UserId,
        MAX(ur.CreatedOn) AS CreatedOn,
        STRING_AGG(r.Name, ', ') AS RoleName
    FROM [pims].[dbo].[UserRoles] ur
    INNER JOIN Roles r ON ur.RoleId = r.Id
    GROUP BY ur.UserId
) AS urd ON u.Id = urd.UserId

LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT UserId, MIN(AgencyId) AS AgencyId
    FROM UserAgencies
    GROUP BY UserId
) ua_min ON u.Id = ua_min.UserId
LEFT OUTER JOIN UserAgencies ua ON u.Id = ua.UserId AND ua.AgencyId = ua_min.AgencyId

WHERE u.Id <> '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'

GROUP BY u.[Id],
    u.[CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    u.CreatedOn, 
    urd.UserId, 
    ua.AgencyId
ORDER BY u.CreatedOn, u.UpdatedOn
